Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:35.99,Ep Title,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,Dog Food Doesn't Have As \NMuch Flavor As You'd Think
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.75,0:01:43.38,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What's that look for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.38,0:01:44.77,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Got a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.21,0:01:47.67,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If it's not enough, eat the meatballs \Non the bottoms of your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:47.65,Meatball,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,meatball (paw pads)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.07,0:01:49.55,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Sadaharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.55,0:01:51.38,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to make do with this today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:54.65,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Odd Jobs is going through \Na food shortage right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.65,0:01:56.42,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,We're all starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:00.13,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.13,0:02:02.26,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-chan, Sadaharu understands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.63,0:02:03.63,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.63,0:02:06.14,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Then the three of us can split this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.42,0:02:09.77,Main01,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:12.52,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:15.15,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have any human dignity?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:17.95,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't steal food from your \Npet, no matter how hungry you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:19.03,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You should be ashamed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:20.58,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Can you blame us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.58,0:02:22.31,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's been ages since \Nwe last had a client,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:25.11,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,so we don't have a single \Ngrain of rice left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:27.80,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The situation's so grim
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:30.42,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,that we may go from eating dog \Nfood to eating the dog for food.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:31.97,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Eating the dog for food?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:35.13,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You're moving from pissing off the \NPTA to pissing off PETA now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:37.57,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What's that about PETA?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:39.31,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Does the PTA eat PETA?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:42.16,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,The PTA only eats up \Nteachers with an attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:44.14,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That's completely different!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.38,0:02:45.90,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Quit your bitching.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:49.27,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Whose fault do you think this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:53.35,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of this large animal \Nthat eats a lot and never works,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.35,0:02:57.07,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,and the glasses boy who just \Nwears glasses and never works.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:59.46,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You've crossed the line now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:01.20,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize! Apologize to my glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:04.35,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you should \Ntry to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:06.82,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,how hard it is for me to \Ntake care of you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:10.91,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're sporting some \Nyummy-looking wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:12.88,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,They're not wings! \NThey're greasy glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.28,0:03:14.76,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And they're not greasy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.76,0:03:17.13,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,You're wearing shellfish to be fashionable?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:18.63,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Are you supposed to be Takeda Kumiko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:19.49,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:22.01,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,These people are so hungry \Nthat they're hallucinating!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.53,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Hand that over!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:25.32,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:26.18,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Those are my glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:27.60,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You can't eat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:28.57,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:30.16,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you grilling them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:36.51,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You should try to understand how hard \Nit is for me to take care of you all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:57.70,Please,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Please take me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:10.28,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Enough already!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:12.46,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Egg on rice again?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:15.47,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why do you waste food like this?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:18.58,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What food? The fridge was empty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.29,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your head is empty!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:24.75,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sadaharu puts up with the meager \Nservings of cheap food we give him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:26.12,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shut up and eat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:27.10,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, is that so?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:28.14,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here you go then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:31.39,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gin-chan! Sadaharu isn't \Nyour garbage disposal!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:34.10,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And there's no food left \Nif you refuse to eat that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:38.34,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry, but unlike the rest \Nof you, I'm a gourmet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:40.74,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You animals can have your pet food.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.97,0:06:21.36,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:22.68,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:25.14,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you find it, Captain Okita?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:26.28,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Sogo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:29.12,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the Odd Jobs dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.12,0:06:31.18,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if he was \Ndumped or if he ran away,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:32.67,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,but he was urinating in the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.67,0:06:35.29,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, so why did you bring him here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:37.84,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you remember how we screwed up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:39.92,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,the last time we tried to boost \Nour image with a mascot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:41.89,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,We should give it another try.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:44.41,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,We can make some money by dumping him
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:46.46,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,and Hijikata-san at the South Pole
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:47.74,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,and making the one who \Nreturns alive our mascot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:50.43,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,That wouldn't be a mascot! \NIt'd be a scum-cot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:52.49,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:55.85,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need any symbols \Nof weakness like mascots.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:59.52,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we already have a \Nmascot in Kondo-san, you fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:01.75,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,He's no mascot! He's a shit-cot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:04.11,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Who was that?! Who \Ncalled me Ridley Scott?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:04.94,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:06.86,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody had anything \Nnice to say about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:10.15,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,And why do we have to take \Nin their used goods?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:11.30,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,He'll interfere with our work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:12.61,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Get rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:15.88,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Vice-Chief, are you telling us to \Nthrow out this adorable creature?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:17.07,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Adorable, my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:19.09,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you all commit seppuku \Nfor failing as warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:20.83,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Then you throw it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:23.08,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, you fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:31.02,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Kondo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:33.20,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered that we \Ndon't have any police dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:34.68,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,You commit seppuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:35.81,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:37.77,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just saying that \Nwe need police dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:39.65,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing adorable \Nabout this furball!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:43.04,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,First, we'll run some tests to \Nsee if it's qualified enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:45.40,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,And I won't go easy on dogs, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:49.03,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up! Police dogs \Ndepend on their noses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.29,0:07:54.39,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,They need to be able to sniff out \Nsuspects, drugs, and all kinds of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:55.78,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,So here's a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:08:00.11,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Half-fat, quarter-fat, \Nnon-cholesterol, non-oil, mustard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:01.81,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:04.02,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,They're all mayonnaise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:05.98,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you planning on \Nusing these police dogs for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:07.70,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of crime are \Nyou preparing for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:09.74,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,First, identify my favorite type.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:12.09,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, nobody knows what you \Nlike! And nobody cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:14.00,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the quarter-fat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.00,0:08:15.76,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,An excellent choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:18.85,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, I'm in the \Nmood for some non-oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:20.84,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Your preference changes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:22.52,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,But I like your taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:24.08,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:24.77,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:27.27,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,You just wanted to feed \Nthe dog mayonnaise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:29.29,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:30.38,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:32.90,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:40.45,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, there, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:43.36,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I don't know what happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:45.46,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,but you should probably make up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:47.41,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:50.83,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san isn't the kind of person \Nwho would kick you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:54.84,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,You probably left because he \Nwas being nasty as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:09:00.43,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I won't be \Nable to keep you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:03.39,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,You already have a home, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.26,0:09:08.90,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,But if you plan on making up soon, \Nyou can stay here until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:13.91,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let Gin-san's precious \Npet die on the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.54,0:09:19.33,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, that tickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:21.03,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:22.83,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Do you do this with \NGin-san all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:27.13,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could have been \Nborn as Gin-san's pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:28.33,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:31.22,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go make something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:32.56,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,You must be hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:33.38,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:44.88,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,The moment I've been waiting \Nfor has finally come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:48.96,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,This is my chance to \Nbecome Gin-san's pet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:52.94,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,His white fur will be my wedding dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:54.59,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Gin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:58.97,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Your cute pet will be coming \Nback to you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:07.38,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:10.46,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been difficult \Nto have such a lazy owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:14.21,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,But Sadaharu, I knew that \Nyou would wake up one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:17.33,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,The spirit of the Joi burns within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:20.46,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that it would guide \Nyou to your true leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:22.76,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,That you would find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:23.97,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,And that is why
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:26.18,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting here since
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:27.89,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,that game of Kick the Can \Ntwo months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:33.19,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have an episode about \NMaster Shoyo without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:36.26,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to adjust my \Nschedule so I could squeeze in,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:38.90,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,but I didn't expect this to take so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:41.43,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an expert at hiding,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:42.85,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,but it's been so long
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:45.44,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,that I had to wonder if \Nthe game was already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.44,0:10:49.53,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone had even noticed \Nthat I was playing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:51.32,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like crying for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:55.23,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Runaway Kotaro tried a \Nlittle too hard there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:56.92,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I caused everyone so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:11:00.77,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Well, everyone's probably been \Nworried and looking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.77,0:11:01.65,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I should probably head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:06.12,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:09.28,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,After staying in this position for two \Nmonths, my body is stiff as a rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:11.19,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Zabeth, call for a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:14.06,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,How could this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:16.69,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can last long \Nenough for sensei to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:17.92,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sadaharu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:19.27,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:22.20,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to keep my promise \Nto become your owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:25.82,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,And can you please relay a \Nmessage when the doctor comes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:29.36,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him to charge any taxi or \Nany other transportation costs
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:32.46,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,to sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:41.59,Please,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Please take me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:03.86,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see him around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:06.66,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it was a really big dog, \Nso it must have been him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:09.37,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,He was dragging a little puppy around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.24,0:12:11.71,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Sadaharu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:16.29,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Sadaharu, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:18.11,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Say something if you're there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:20.67,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Please come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:22.71,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Sadaharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:41.15,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What? Work?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:43.74,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we finally have a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:45.99,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,No more eating dog food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:48.78,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you supposed to \Nbe looking for Sadaharu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:50.60,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,instead of wasting time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:53.21,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Wasting time? Want me to punch you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.65,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you worried about him, Gin-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:58.71,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Sadaharu hasn't been home in two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.20,0:13:01.13,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,He was starving when he left,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:03.26,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,and we don't know if he's \Ngotten anything to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:04.72,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sadaharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:04.72,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,or if something's happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:07.90,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,How can you expect us to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:09.72,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Come back, Sadaharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:09.72,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good, Shinpachi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:11.88,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking like a NEET now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:15.12,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:15.67,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:19.29,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,He left because he \Ncouldn't get any food.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:20.61,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:25.46,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,An animal doesn't understand \Nthe concept of family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:27.49,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:30.87,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in keeping \Nanyone around who isn't
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:32.41,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,willing to share when times are tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:33.70,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he's just an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:35.68,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:38.44,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If you like dog food, you can eat \Nit for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:41.33,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go make some money and \Nhave a chocolate parfait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.33,0:13:43.71,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, Gin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:45.40,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:47.97,Animal,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Edo Animal Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.21,0:13:49.68,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mononoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:53.07,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,The dog god Moro has come \Nto hunt down our patients!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:54.49,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Scram, mountain dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.49,0:13:56.34,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,This is where humans live!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:13:58.46,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Mononoke should go back \Nto the mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:04.05,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,It released something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:04.89,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:06.74,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die if you touch that stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:23.34,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sadaharu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:34.37,Collar,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(918,1)}1 Fourth St.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:45.94,Fourth,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(501,1)}1 Fourth St.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.22,0:14:49.41,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So the owner of this house is dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:51.74,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he died all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:55.87,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,He kept a lot of dogs, and there were
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:59.29,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,many complaints from the neighbors \Nabout the smell and noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.68,0:15:03.37,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,There was a relative who liked \Ndogs and visited occasionally,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:06.30,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,but it appears that they grew distant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:08.84,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,And the number of dogs was declining.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:12.16,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,There was only one left when he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:13.96,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,When the neighborhood association \Ncleaned his place,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:16.31,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,she didn't know what to do \Nwith it, so she threw it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:22.48,Main01,D,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, it was a mutt, sick and \Nfrail, so nobody wanted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:26.94,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,There have been rumors that \Nhe's been wandering around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:29.99,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,We've been receiving complaints \Nfrom various pet owners.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:32.49,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,They're worried it may \Nget their pets sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:37.00,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,So could you catch it and \Ndispose of it for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:41.37,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Is that even necessary? It probably \Ndied already if it was sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:45.00,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so, but if we wait for it to \Nbecome a problem, it'll be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:48.18,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,If it's dying anyway, does it matter \Nif it happens a little sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:49.38,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:53.01,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,That old man left us a \Nbig mess to clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:58.06,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's this huge dog?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:01.25,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:04.03,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This stray's bigger than I was expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:06.57,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take some effort to dispose of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:09.54,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You know the puppy they're \Ntalking about, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:12.57,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If you turn it over, \NI'll let you come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:17.04,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The reward will buy us plenty of \Nfood, so everyone will be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:18.25,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Do you see a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:23.69,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:26.72,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Odd Jobs, catch that monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:29.96,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you standing there? \NHurry up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:38.51,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you turn it over, \NI'll let you come home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:05.42,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then the three of us can split this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:57.70,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,It stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:18:58.72,Main01,D,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:00.34,Main01,D,0000,0000,0000,,Who would do such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:02.83,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,So many fish...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:05.77,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It was our dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:09.78,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like he was taking \Ncare of that puppy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:13.17,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,so I tampered with the \Nfood he was bringing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:15.52,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Look. See this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:18.80,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,My dog is very bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:24.68,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,He fed the puppy poisoned \Nfood to do my job for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:29.16,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So can you pay up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:37.07,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:43.07,General,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,General Animal Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:39.10,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You were suffering from malnutrition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:43.68,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,They told me I shouldn't have \Na pet if I can't feed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:47.83,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Although you're the one who \Nran off and starved yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:51.83,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But you helped deal \Nwith the puppy for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:56.09,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You can eat all you want today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:01.45,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:04.05,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might understand \Nhow it feels to be an owner
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:05.81,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,after taking care of that puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:08.34,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Were you hoping for fish tails?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:13.90,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Or is the portion too small, \Nconsidering the reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:15.78,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:18.76,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,There were a lot of expenses \Nassociated with this job,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:21.14,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,so I used up most of \Nthe money we received.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.14,0:20:25.89,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, the Sakata family always \Nshares when times are tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:28.87,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We share the food
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.26,0:20:32.44,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,and the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:39.42,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for sharing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:45.43,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:47.92,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,You kept Grandpa's dog safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:51.43,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you should thank \Nthe big dog inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:58.36,Main01,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:02.64,Main01,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't paid for all the \Nmedicine you fed the puppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:03.99,Main01,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:08.34,Main01,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Sakata-san! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.37,0:23:37.63,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.63,0:23:39.14,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What's this Final Act business?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.14,0:23:40.14,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,This is news to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.14,0:23:44.02,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they're probably just fooling \Naround again with a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.02,0:23:45.45,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Or they're pretending that it's fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.45,0:23:46.12,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Or it is fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.12,0:23:47.10,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's what they want you to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.10,0:23:48.33,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,But it's really fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.33,0:23:49.94,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You're not making any sense at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.97,0:23:54.29,Side Bar Top,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,We only lasted half a year this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.97,0:23:54.29,Side Bar Bottom,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,but thank you for all the support.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.29,0:23:59.94,Side Bar Top,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,The movie is coming up in July,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.29,0:23:59.94,Side Bar Bottom,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,so please continue to support Gintama!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.94,0:24:04.67,Side Bar Top,,0000,0000,0000,,See you sometime...
